      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       nor-pre-rig-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se record non New : nessuna azione              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-new        =    spaces
                     go to nor-pre-rig-999.
       nor-pre-rig-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del tipo sezione         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-sez (1)    =    "P    "
                     perform nor-pre-rig-pre-000
                                          thru nor-pre-rig-pre-999
           else if   w-rig-tip-sez (1)    =    "ERARI"
                     perform nor-pre-rig-era-000
                                          thru nor-pre-rig-era-999
           else if   w-rig-tip-sez (1)    =    "INPS "
                     perform nor-pre-rig-ips-000
                                          thru nor-pre-rig-ips-999
           else if   w-rig-tip-sez (1)    =    "REGIO"
                     perform nor-pre-rig-rgn-000
                                          thru nor-pre-rig-rgn-999
           else if   w-rig-tip-sez (1)    =    "ENLOC"
                     perform nor-pre-rig-enl-000
                                          thru nor-pre-rig-enl-999
           else if   w-rig-tip-sez (1)    =    "INAIL"
                     perform nor-pre-rig-inl-000
                                          thru nor-pre-rig-inl-999
           else if   w-rig-tip-sez (1)    =    "ENPRE"
                     perform nor-pre-rig-enp-000
                                          thru nor-pre-rig-enp-999
           else if   w-rig-tip-sez (1)    =    "C    "
                     perform nor-pre-rig-zzz-000
                                          thru nor-pre-rig-zzz-999
           else      go to nor-pre-rig-999.
       nor-pre-rig-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
