           move      spaces               to   w-rig-fir-maa (1)      .
           move      zero                 to   w-rig-dat-pre (1)      .
           move      zero                 to   w-rig-cod-int (1)      .
           move      spaces               to   w-rig-cod-int-rag (1)  .
       nor-pre-rig-pre-999.
