           move      spaces               to   w-rig-pos-inl (1)      .
           move      spaces               to   w-rig-ccp-inl (1)      .
           move      spaces               to   w-rig-rif-inl (1)      .
           move      spaces               to   w-rig-cau-inl (1)      .
           move      spaces               to   w-rig-cau-inl-des (1)  .
