      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-pre-acc-ins      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di presentazione           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-sez-pre (1)      .
       pre-acc-ins-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Attribuzione numero protocollo                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiamo subroutine                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-dat-reg        to   w-att-mpu-prt-ddo      .
           perform   att-mpu-prt-000      thru att-mpu-prt-999        .
           move      w-att-mpu-prt-num    to   w-tes-num-prt          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
