      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-dup-rec-flg    =    spaces
                     go to pre-acc-ins-500.
       pre-acc-ins-410.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se richiesta la duplicazione                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Da buffer a 'w-tes'                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-val-aep (2)    to   w-tes-val-aep (1)      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
