                    (w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr)   to   l-cge-300-dar-ave      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Importo movimento                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      w-wrt-mov-cge-imp
                    (w-wrt-mov-cge-ctr)   to   l-cge-300-imp-mov      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Flag di regime fiscale particolare      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-flg-rfp      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Sigla numerazione                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   l-cge-300-sgl-num      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Data acquisizione                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   l-cge-300-dat-acq      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiamo sottoprogramma per aggiornamenti   *
      *                  * contabili                                   *
