      *              * Lettura record personalizzazioni                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "CODGEP    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      10                   to   rf-gep-tip-gep         .
           move      "SIA       "         to   rf-gep-cod-gep         .
           move      "pgm/gep/fls/ioc/obj/iofgep"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
